{"tid":2055971,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"教育界清算正式開始！左派極紅香島中學政治迫害黃絲老師","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T19:32:03.000Z","uid":110749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a10a794dbda2f88b2d2949d2c32259e37eebe6a","tid":2055971,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ambGMN6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FambGMN6.jpg&h=081f9023&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SH67Hmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSH67Hmr.jpg&h=dd2b6269&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFBPbeN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFBPbeN.jpg&h=0213a0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLgrXUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLgrXUN.jpg&h=64da813a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNJFhUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNJFhUN.jpg&h=a5ef35ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHADO1t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHADO1t.jpg&h=6aca16e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UXeX4zO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUXeX4zO.jpg&h=233b6905&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSPdCUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSPdCUP.jpg&h=d62527d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpFDO1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpFDO1v.jpg&h=d5c53195&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hg5oZ8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHg5oZ8c.jpg&h=7ec371e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpMvE8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpMvE8f.jpg&h=97c81e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於李筠佩老師於今天發的公開信，本關注組作出以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣：老師曾向校方解釋老師認為當中有的誤會，但校方都沒有接納她的解釋，只針對她的政治理念而作出批判，事前亦都沒有任何警告或者意見，令到老師感受到前所未有的白色恐怖，本關注組不能理解為什麼校方可以不接納老師的意見，而政治中立是否代表校方的政治正確。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣：老師嚴格遵守教育局提出的指引，不將政治帶入校園，而老師亦都沒有違反教育局的指引，老師卻遭到校方的解雇，而當中原因是因為政治立場，校方曾多次向關注組表示不將政治帶入校園的要求，導致多次校園罷課活動未能成功進行，如今不攻自破，試問校方不將政治帶入校園的理解是什麼，希望校方可以向關注組作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ ：當中老師是因為政治立場與學校相反而被解僱，如果跟學校政治立場相同的話，是否可以橫行霸道，希望校方可以正面回應大眾困惑<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣：學生選擇歌曲考試並非老師選擇，而學校亦都沒有就歌曲「黑名單」，二老師亦都提醒學生需要小心謹慎去選擇歌曲，但校方仍不接納老師的解釋。<br />\n<br />\n本關注組對老師被政治原因解僱，甚至政治打壓，表達無奈及憤慨，希望校方能夠理解本關注組對此事的憤慨及大眾對此事的看法，並認真反思當中校方做錯的決定，本關注組亦希望可以跟校方溝通，之後日子可能會跟校方再次溝通。<br />\n<br />\n香島中學本土關注組"},{"pid":"5c63e53dc3caa695616d8d66d32a5a6c24d68e30","tid":2055971,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178e19dc4f3b26856dada2e548a9c5694fd598c8","tid":2055971,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59312c3046fddeea73f10ee0171eb63edcf31273","tid":2055971,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0f52004e85ee8049b3496b61765c390a7dbf3825","tid":2055971,"uid":314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1364048695f14a92add8f8f0708b5a80fc857d9a","tid":2055971,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f0315d080759356188019d4de113a3ae825113","tid":2055971,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fc9295c34566e3ac83a5fbbd38b3db13d0268ff5","tid":2055971,"uid":163809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d8df2e10997a13d4642d7d4f4a3a73a91ab5514","tid":2055971,"uid":357118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T19:32:03.000Z","msg":"14年香島都好似有老師因政見問題比人逼走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}